      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Dana Wallet主动发起订阅。然后当Bitcoin Core Node产生新区块时，先推送给Blindbit-Oracle，Oracle内部要做几件事：计算tweak、索引unspent outputs，然后才通知Scanner。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bitcoin Core Node",
        "Blindbit-Oracle",
        "New Block",
        "compute tweak",
        "index unspent outputs"
