      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先把主线画出来。Dana Wallet用虚线箭头订阅Blindbit-Oracle的新区块，BC到BP是新区块推送，BP内部加了两个note标注计算tweak和索引UTXO。接下来Oracle还要做什么处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Dana Wallet",
        "Blindbit-Oracle",
