    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Oracle内部还有三步自循环：compute tweak、compute spent、build taproot GCS filter。做完这些才用虚线箭头把new block推送给Scanner。然后Scanner会分两次请求：先请求tweaks和UTXOs，再请求filters。",
